   *(Note: "kui doe" = 個頭 (head/top). "9" = 就 (just) or 九 (nine)? In Chinglish, "9" often means "就" (jiu) or "九" (nine). "ng" = 我 (me). "connect" = connect. "8 ge" = 8個 (8 items).
