   Translation: **個頭就我connect 8個，唔個一樣呀個有打大樣**

9. **need boot gei, wait me, ng hoe hoi chi ju**
   => 需要boot幾，等我，我開機去
   *(Note: "need" = 需要. "boot" = boot. "gei" = 幾 (how long). "wait me" = 等我. "ng" = 我. "hoe" = 開 (open). "hoi" = 開 (open). "chi" = 機 (machine/computer). "ju" = 去 (go).
   "ng hoe hoi chi ju" -> 我開機去 (I go turn on the computer).
   "need boot gei" -> 需要boot幾 (Need to boot how long?)
   Translation: **需要boot幾，等我，我開機去** (How long to boot, wait for me, I go turn on the computer.)

